@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Capetropolis";
}

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1, shrink-to-fit=no" />
    <title>@ViewData["Title"] - Capetropolis</title>
    <link href="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
    <style>
        body {
            background-image: url('@Url.Content("~/wwwroot/Images/POOL.jpg")'); /* Replace with your background image path */
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            background-attachment: fixed;
            color: #fff;
        }
        .content-container {
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7); /* Semi-transparent background for readability */
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 10px;
        }
        .card-body {
            color: #000; /* Set the color of the hotel name and information to black */
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container mt-5 content-container">
        <div class="text-center mb-5">
            <h1>About Capetropolis</h1>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-4">
            <h2>The Founding of Capetropolis</h2>
            <p>
                Capetropolis was founded in 1850 by a group of entrepreneurs who were drawn to the area's natural beauty and strategic location.
                The city's founders, led by a wealthy businessman named Marcus Thompson, envisioned a luxurious resort town that would cater to the elite of society.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-4">
            <h2>The Golden Age</h2>
            <p>
                During the late 19th and early 20th centuries, Capetropolis experienced a golden age of growth and development. The city became a popular destination
                for the wealthy and famous, who were drawn to its stunning beaches, luxurious hotels, and vibrant cultural scene. The city's economy flourished, and
                it became known as the "Jewel of the Coast."
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-4">
            <h2>The War Years</h2>
            <p>
                During World War II, Capetropolis played an important role in the war effort. The city's strategic location made it an ideal spot for military bases
                and supply depots. The city's residents rallied around the war effort, and many served in the military or worked in the war industry.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-4">
            <h2>Post-War Era</h2>
            <p>
                After the war, Capetropolis continued to grow and develop. The city became a popular destination for tourists, and its economy continued to thrive.
                In the 1960s and 1970s, the city experienced a cultural renaissance, with the establishment of numerous art galleries, museums, and performance venues.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-4">
            <h2>Modern Era</h2>
            <p>
                Today, Capetropolis is a thriving city that is known for its stunning natural beauty, rich history, and vibrant cultural scene. The city is home to
                five luxurious hotels, each with its own unique character and charm. Visitors to Capetropolis can enjoy a wide range of activities, from water sports
                and outdoor adventures to cultural attractions and fine dining.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="mb-4">
            <h2>Our Luxurious Hotels</h2>
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                        <img src="@Url.Content("~/wwwroot/Images/HOTEL1.jpg")" class="card-img-top" alt="Hotel 1">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">CapeSweet</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Experience the ultimate in luxury and comfort at The Grand Capetropolis Hotel, located in the heart of the city.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                        <img src="@Url.Content("~/wwwroot/Images/HOTEL2.jpg")" class="card-img-top" alt="Hotel 2">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">CapeIvory</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Enjoy breathtaking ocean views and top-notch amenities at the Oceanview Resort.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                        <img src="@Url.Content("~/wwwroot/Images/HOTEL3.jpg")" class="card-img-top" alt="Hotel 3">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">CapeHive</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Indulge in the regal elegance of Capetropolis Palace, a favorite among dignitaries and celebrities.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                        <img src="@Url.Content("~/wwwroot/Images/HOTEL4.jpg")" class="card-img-top" alt="Hotel 4">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">CapeHoney</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Relax in style at the Sunset Boulevard Hotel, known for its stunning sunset views and luxurious accommodations.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="card mb-4 shadow-sm">
                        <img src="@Url.Content("~/wwwroot/Images/HOTEL5.jpg")" class="card-img-top" alt="Hotel 5">
                        <div class="card-body">
                            <h5 class="card-title">CapeCrow</h5>
                            <p class="card-text">Discover the charm of the Harbor Lights Inn, a boutique hotel offering personalized service and elegant rooms.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
    <script src="https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.5.1.slim.min.js"></script>
    <script src="https://stackpath.bootstrapcdn.com/bootstrap/4.5.2/js/bootstrap.min.js"></script>
</body>
</html>
